{"tid":1937474,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"環球時報轟廣東省未隔離港澳台 破壞中國抗疫成果","createTime":"2020-03-22T02:53:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-22T07:53:16.000Z","uid":19552,"like":286,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":140,"replies":[{"pid":"bc351c69cf167413b3feea712cc4185fc9b52015","tid":1937474,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T02:53:54.000Z","msg":"內地新冠肺炎控疫部署，改為嚴防境外疫情輸入風險，廣東對境外入粵人士，一律隔離14天集中隔離觀察，不包括港澳台。官媒《環球時報》總編輯胡錫進今晨在微博發文砲轟廣東省這一入境隔離新規，點名香港、台灣近日病例激增，形勢尤其危險，各地政府絕不能網開一面，導致內地面臨第二次感染的巨大風險，應一視同仁隔離台港澳入境人士。<br />\n<br />\n點名香港台灣病例激增　形勢尤其危險<br />\n<br />\n廣東省政府今晨宣布，自3月21日0時起，對所有從境外（不含港澳台）經廣東口岸入境的人員，以及經港澳台地區和省外口岸入境來粵且來粵前14天內有國外旅居史的人員，其目的地為廣東的，無論外國公民還是中國公民，廣東均一視同仁，一律實施14天居家或集中隔離醫學觀察。<br />\n<br />\n對此，胡錫進21日凌晨在微博發文質疑「廣東省的這個新規是什麼意思？是港澳台入粵人員可以不隔離嗎？」如果是這樣，他表示反對。<br />\n<br />\n胡錫進微博原文：<br />\n<br />\n廣東省的這個新規是什麼意思？是港澳台入粵人員可以不隔離嗎？如果是這樣，老胡作為內地媒體人表示反對。<br />\n<br />\n港澳台與內地是不同的抗疫管理體系，有不同的檢測標準，港台近日病例激增，形勢尤其危險，決不能對從那裡進入內地的人網開一面。<br />\n<br />\n那樣將使剛剛本土新增病例歸零的內地面臨第二次感染的巨大風險。呼籲廣東省重新考慮這個政策，大疫當前，內地的安全第一，其他都應排在之後。"},{"pid":"80ef1f96d24b28650b137581cf1f2aa244c3d814","tid":1937474,"uid":19552,"like":62,"dislike":3,"score":59,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T02:54:35.000Z","msg":"網民留言支持 「堅決不能放開港台」<br />\n<br />\n胡錫進昨晚發文表示，據他瞭解，現在對香港來的人是否隔離以及怎麼隔離，權限完全在地方政府的手裡，對集中隔離擴展到多少國家和地區，決定權也在各地方政府的手裡。他拜託各地政府不要再猶豫，及時把集中隔離的措施擴大到「中國大陸境外所有國家和地區來的人」，強調「現在已經到了必須這樣做的時候」。<br />\n<br />\n有網民留言表示支持和認同，稱「堅決不能放開港台」、「骨子裡還是作賤自己，非得搞什麼惠台惠港政策」、「他們在考慮什麼啊？廣東政府是親英還是親美？」、「廣東瘋了，如果這樣，建議其他省份對所有來自廣東的人進行隔離」，也有人認為「國家應該統一規定，現在各省都自己的標準，有點亂」。"},{"pid":"fbcaaf54c9a1617136b62f2305276a951f6e6b32","tid":1937474,"uid":324229,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T02:55:11.000Z","msg":"突發 3個拒絕隔離人士資料被公開 入黎打比衛生署檢舉同報狗<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1937467\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1937467</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7ee611bd62017c16c4c462adf3fc771d1506d29e","tid":1937474,"uid":254028,"like":202,"dislike":0,"score":202,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T02:55:54.000Z","msg":"On99 你估香港好想接收你哋班人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n根本就唔應該比佢哋坐飛機嚟香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞到香港依家變咗一個輸出嘅地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4e53ce994628986d156eeac74e48e6030ceb280","tid":1937474,"uid":155095,"like":127,"dislike":0,"score":127,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T02:56:28.000Z","msg":"又話港澳台係中國不可分割嘅一部份 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e95658e65392c552632d4393f7dc40e4cf9b25a4","tid":1937474,"uid":152476,"like":91,"dislike":0,"score":91,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T02:56:58.000Z","msg":"不是一家人啦？<br />\n不是中國香港啦？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a988dba3f372ca2e12b4a04e857a1afeb74c6f7","tid":1937474,"uid":235501,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T02:56:59.000Z","msg":"係就快手"},{"pid":"bc5a807b83e2f03e21f9a9f71b91664ef5a2bc16","tid":1937474,"uid":19552,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"quote":{"pid":"b4e53ce994628986d156eeac74e48e6030ceb280","tid":1937474,"uid":155095,"like":127,"dislike":0,"score":127,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T02:56:28.000Z","msg":"又話港澳台係中國不可分割嘅一部份 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T02:57:11.000Z","msg":"想推班支那留學生比香港食"},{"pid":"1018641b7b27da8d0412c089d386a0fac4f96ffe","tid":1937474,"uid":112622,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T02:57:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4a27bc14b780e585efc32ce66e8038dc60bc808c","tid":1937474,"uid":132287,"like":143,"dislike":0,"score":143,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T02:59:48.000Z","msg":"果時自己日日枱面上7，8000宗果時又屌人封你關歧視<br />\n到惹到人地中哂招之後果時就大大聲屌柒人傳染比你<br />\n人無恥則無敵"},{"pid":"20cf73346d4b0d5d5c6a2336a36a927da74f8149","tid":1937474,"uid":23085,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T03:01:20.000Z","msg":"最驚你唔封<br />\n封啦 封啦<br />\n唔封正契弟"},{"pid":"262dce5b7b4adedf907608101c8fdeedbed2267b","tid":1937474,"uid":198829,"like":56,"dislike":0,"score":56,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T03:01:21.000Z","msg":"搞清楚先<br />\n係你地中國人要經香港返中國"},{"pid":"b85293299e9b43dc46df32203c4b3748b5ac8670","tid":1937474,"uid":198829,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"262dce5b7b4adedf907608101c8fdeedbed2267b","tid":1937474,"uid":198829,"like":56,"dislike":0,"score":56,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T03:01:21.000Z","msg":"搞清楚先<br />\n係你地中國人要經香港返中國"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T03:02:58.000Z","msg":"哥時要求封，班中國人就話港獨"},{"pid":"ed7ee2c485abdeee5347942ad878d1e5358a5224","tid":1937474,"uid":225798,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T03:02:59.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a235a82c0eac76180531b5a58d8540772d86fc41","tid":1937474,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T03:03:15.000Z","msg":"快d封"},{"pid":"252d87d2872202d1c58e5e13da66c7c758597dac","tid":1937474,"uid":79562,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T03:03:16.000Z","msg":"新增個案零<br />\n湖北解封<br />\n但唔俾湖北人去北京<br />\n只可以去其他地方<br />\n（中略）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【湖北出城指數新高，主要去廣東，大家小心】為配合全國復工復產，湖北出城指數創下近期疫情新高，更首次超過去年規模（年初二起計）。<br />\n<br />\n武漢自封城後，自年初二起，湖北出城人流明顯大幅下降，大都只剩去年同期的零頭。自從習近平3月10日視察武漢後，形勢變得一片大好，湖北新增個案「歸零」，隨後出省指數持續上升。<br />\n<br />\n3月19日，湖北出城指數達4.76，比去年同期的4.4為高，是首次超越去年同期（自年初二以來），顯示湖北已經「正常化」，但信不信由你。<br />\n<br />\n這些湖北人流的目的地，近四成是去廣東省，以東莞、深圳、廣州、惠州居多，從廣東返港隔離人士要多注意。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：百度地圖慧眼大數據<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/03/22/KtHjJ3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F03%2F22%2FKtHjJ3.png&h=ea947565&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/03/22/vhDTM6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F03%2F22%2FvhDTM6.png&h=f3721ba8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/03/22/nLI8Ox.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F03%2F22%2FnLI8Ox.png&h=14efdf38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n來源：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/489997741184811/posts/1377592979091945/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F489997741184811%2Fposts%2F1377592979091945%2F&d=HaOdbOSPDN3vR1kWeckjcFEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=4dbbfc68\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/489997741184811/posts/1377592979091945/</a>"},{"pid":"6bc9489f8cdcf307789ae62dcbd1f2aa5feeaefb","tid":1937474,"uid":6132,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T03:03:22.000Z","msg":"快<br />\n成班支那人仲靠緊香港去深圳"},{"pid":"15e58879801d198fc14ca6639dfd9b46ca6fa889","tid":1937474,"uid":89752,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T03:10:09.000Z","msg":"唔封正契弟<br />\n香港加油直飛武漢"},{"pid":"d685c07b550f1b60246d3cda0054bb1e3a14aa9b","tid":1937474,"uid":213747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T03:10:11.000Z","msg":"收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55d89221d6af56e75624af3f6b26ea1175be40a3","tid":1937474,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T03:10:25.000Z","msg":"快D封<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e2d1b603348289daa2f280342e7741cbb05c273","tid":1937474,"uid":126648,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,