,"tid":1937474,"uid":79562,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T03:03:16.000Z","msg":"新增個案零<br />\n湖北解封<br />\n但唔俾湖北人去北京<br />\n只可以去其他地方<br />\n（中略）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【湖北出城指數新高，主要去廣東，大家小心】為配合全國復工復產，湖北出城指數創下近期疫情新高，更首次超過去年規模（年初二起計）。<br />\n<br />\n武漢自封城後，自年初二起，湖北出城人流明顯大幅下降，大都只剩去年同期的零頭。自從習近平3月10日視察武漢後，形勢變得一片大好，湖北新增個案「歸零」，隨後出省指數持續上升。<br />\n<br />\n3月19日，湖北出城指數達4.76，比去年同期的4.4為高，是首次超越去年同期（自年初二以來），顯示湖北已經「正常化」，但信不信由你。<br />\n<br />\n這些湖北人流的目的地，近四成是去廣東省，以東莞、深圳、廣州、惠州居多，從廣東返港隔離人士要多注意。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：百度地圖慧眼大數據<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/03/22/KtHjJ3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F03%2F22%2FKtHjJ3.png&h=ea947565&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/03/22/vhDTM6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F03%2F22%2FvhDTM6.png&h=f3721ba8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/03/22/nLI8Ox.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F03%2F22%2FnLI8Ox.png&h=14efdf38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n來源：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/489997741184811/posts/1377592979091945/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F489997741184811%2Fposts%2F1377592979091945%2F&d=HaOdbOSPDN3vR1kWeckjcFEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=4dbbfc68\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/489997741184811/posts/1377592979091945/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T04:22:24.000Z","msg":"三成去廣東"},{"pid":"0197260fbff805be32ad12c5a2873bb3e8f3f1ab","tid":1937474,"uid":158457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T04:22:40.000Z","msg":"有著數就攬<br />\n搞破壞就割<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72b53d97ffbfac7f89e434731b9cd168f2c8e115","tid":1937474,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T